Twitter Client Library for Qt C++
(C) 2010 Soluvas <http://www.Soluvas.com>
Project Home: http://gitorious.org/qtwitterclient
Blog: http://qt-mobility.blogspot.com/search/label/QTwitterClient
Licensed under LGPL version 2.1

Client library for Twitter.

Usage:

    QTwitterClient *twitter = new QTwitterClient(this);
    twitter->setLogin(login);
    twitter->setPassword(password);

    twitter->tweet("I feel really good today!");

Geotagging support:

    twitter->tweetGeo("Guess where I am right now?",
        45.93481948,    // longitude
        -79.28399284);  // latitude
